Usage: filter_collection [-help] <base_collection> <filter_expression>
                         [-nocase] [-quiet] [-regexp]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<base_collection>     # Collection of objects from which to filter objects for
                      # the new collection (string, required)
<filter_expression>   # Criteria with which to filter objects
                      # (string, required)
-nocase               # Specifies that pattern matching is not case sensitive.
                      # (bool, optional)
-quiet                # Suppresses all error and warning messages generated
                      # when the filter_collection command is run (bool, optional)
-regexp               # Treats the specified patterns as regular expression
                      # patterns. (bool, optional)